            <li><span class="versione_alpha">v0.1</span> first draft. MongoDB backend to store invoices metadata, API to add/query invoices, external documents on filesystem, logging, localizations (server only) and some code to accomodate the app behind a reverse proxy.</li>
          </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="col-lg-1 col-md-1"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div id="team" class="tab-pane fade in">
